Vale May Name Barbosa as Chairman, Replacing Flores, Veja Says

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-04-09T16:19:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/vale-may-name-barbosa-as-chairman-replacing-flores-veja-says.html
Vale SA (VALE3)  may name Brazil Deputy
Finance Minister Nelson Barbosa to replace Ricardo Flores as
chairman,  Veja  magazine said in its Holofote column, without
saying where it got the information.  Chief Executive Officer Roger Agnelli, who leaves the
company next month, may start an asset management company, Veja
said, without citing anyone.  Murilo Pinto de Oliveira Ferreira will become Vale CEO on
May 22, the company said April 4.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in  Sao Paulo  at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 